review: Robinsson palace is a beautiful property just outside of Mukteswar. Rooms are large and luxurious and have all the required amenities. Beautiful view of himalayas from rooms. Food is also very goo. Service is awesome. Thanks to Mr. Anand Goswami for booking this for us. Anand ji is the most reliable person for Kumayun tour starting from cabs to hotels, he will take care of the entire tour.
